data.text: The AFL Record finals editions has all aspects of the AFL game covered with fans able to access a special 24-page match-day section featuring the return of selected teams and player lists. The Week 1 Finals edition includes: • A panel of SEN experts preview the four big finals – and they name the players to watch and discuss the stats that matter. • Scott Pendlebury will move into equal-seventh place on the all-time finals list. We catch up with the Collingwood star who joins AFL legends Leigh Matthews, Bruce Doull and Wayne Schimmelbusch on 29 finals appearances. • Team lists and stats for all eight clubs. • Dedicated covers for all four finals The Week 1 Finals edition will be on sale at the MCG and the Gabba for $10. To subscribe to the AFL Record, visit aflrecord.com.au
